RULES:
- Every section must have specific key_points (not vague descriptions)
- Every causal chain must have concrete winners/losers (name companies)
- Flag ALL single-source claims in evidence_quality_flags
- Prefer primary sources (arxiv papers, official announcements) over secondary
- If a claim is speculative, flag it — do not publish it as fact
- Historical comparisons must reference specific past events with dates
- Tables must have actual data, not placeholders
- Return ONLY JSON. No prose.
